'''Polpians''' were one of the many animals sold at the [[Exoticalia Pet Emporium]]. Polpians were relatively small creatures that were often sold as pets. Most [[Bothan/Legends|Bothans]] were allergic to polpians.<ref name="Vision of the Future" />

